    <details>
      <summary>How do I register as a seller on Blinkit?</summary>
      <div class="ans">Blinkit seller registration involves setting up a registered business with GST, preparing your documents (PAN, cancelled cheque, FSSAI for food, trademark, digital signature), submitting the seller application and KYC, getting Category Manager approval, creating your catalog, and sending inventory to go live. IARDO handles this entire registration process for you.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Can I sell on Blinkit without GST?</summary>
      <div class="ans">No. A valid GSTIN is mandatory to register as a seller on Blinkit. If you don&rsquo;t have GST yet, IARDO can guide you through obtaining it as part of onboarding.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>How long does Blinkit seller approval take?</summary>
      <div class="ans">Document and application review can move quickly when everything is in order, but full go-live &mdash; including Category Manager approval, multi-state GST, and sending inventory &mdash; typically takes around 60 working days. Well-prepared brands go live faster; the biggest delays come from document mismatches and pending FSSAI.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Do I need an FSSAI licence to sell on Blinkit?</summary>
      <div class="ans">Yes, if you sell any food, grocery, or consumable products, an FSSAI licence is mandatory. Non-food categories do not require FSSAI. IARDO helps arrange the right licences for your category.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Is there a registration fee to sell on Blinkit?</summary>
      <div class="ans">Blinkit itself does not charge a registration fee to become a seller &mdash; you pay commission and applicable platform fees on orders. IARDO&rsquo;s onboarding engagement is separate and covers the entire setup, and it is fully refundable if your account does not go live.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Which cities does IARDO cover for Blinkit onboarding?</summary>
      <div class="ans">IARDO provides Blinkit onboarding services across PAN India, including Delhi, Mumbai, Bangalore, Hyderabad, Pune, Chennai, Kolkata, Gurgaon, Noida, Ahmedabad, and more. We&rsquo;re based in Rohini, Delhi, and coordinate onboarding and inventory across regions.</div>
    </details>
  </div>
